title: HUCK SPAULDING THE ART OF TATTOOING DVD ISO
description:
This DVD is for instructional and informational purposes only. 

In this DVD, you will find 90 minutes of footage showing: 

color work 
all black work 
and cover up work. 
Also, it will explain: 

stencil making 
machine set-up 
and all the other basics of tattooing 
You will be one-on-one with the artist, and you will learn the basic techniques of the Art of Tattooing.
